    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/3069605c1dfc5f2477ed18531e49c6ad.webp?t=1764719962\" width=616 height=27 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/3a9e5878d122924c5ae4f2ef415d7b2d.poster.avif?t=1764719962\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/3a9e5878d122924c5ae4f2ef415d7b2d.webm?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/3a9e5878d122924c5ae4f2ef415d7b2d.mp4?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match two identical monsters hiding inside  <strong>tombstones</strong> to score points and unleash powerful monster effects upon your enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match all of your monster pairs before your enemy does and get awesome rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/89f2d3fb2ebed27fc9af50dec44d50f5.webp?t=1764719962\" width=616 height=27 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/7599f1b319a8cf2827af564e963844df.poster.avif?t=1764719962\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/7599f1b319a8cf2827af564e963844df.webm?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/7599f1b319a8cf2827af564e963844df.mp4?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle in three game modes: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Prove your worth in fast-paced PvP battles against players around the world;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Conquer the Campaign mode and find unique challenges and rewards within; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Survive the Roguelike mode and try out new strategies every run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/95b28ae649f7ba61f49d0bb59a52b078.webp?t=1764719962\" width=616 height=27 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/ee667733cabe57ceb4be4206575be2c1.poster.avif?t=1764719962\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/ee667733cabe57ceb4be4206575be2c1.webm?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/ee667733cabe57ceb4be4206575be2c1.mp4?t=1764719962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect new monsters and unleash  terror on your enemies. Every monster has a unique effect that can become even stronger when you infuse them with a <strong>Dark Pact</strong> charge.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are four classes to choose from when picking your monster squad: <strong>Slasher, Curser, Invoker, Alchemist</strong>. Picking the right monsters can enable many possible archetypes such as: <strong>Combo, Speed, Freeze, Ramp, Mismatch, Trap etc</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can collect monsters in a number of ways, through alchemy, digging them up in the Necropolis or as a gift from the Collector. Unlock many customizable options for each monster and alter their appearance: <strong>VFX, SFX, jump scare variations etc</strong>.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/ba720f559c94d70e7d39d6b4d6cb756d.webp?t=1764719962\" width=616 height=27 /></span></p>",
